Splendid Bacon
===============

Install Notes
-------------

  1. Host Url is the host at which you are hosting Splendid Bacon. For example splendidbacon.herokuapp.com.
  2. Token is your project token from Splendid Bacon. This is found on the project edit page on your Splendid Bacon host. 
  3. Project ID is a unique identifier for your project. This is found on the project edit page or in any URL for the project.
